    Pathways from MSigDB v7.5.1

    msigdb_pathways.Rd

    Reactome, Gene Ontology (Biological Process, Cellular Component, Molecular Function), and KEGG pathways from version 7.5.1 of the Molecular Signatures Database (MSigDB). Obtained via msigdbr and reformatted. Results filtered to pathways with at least 10 genes.

    data(msigdb_pathways)

    Format

    A data.frame with 8652 rows (pathways) and 4 variables:

    gs_exact_source

    character; unique pathway identifier.

    gs_subcat

    character; the database to which the pathway belongs. One of "GO:BP", "GO:MF", "GO:CC", "CP:REACTOME", or "CP:KEGG".

    gs_description

    character; description of each pathway.

    entrez_gene

    character list; Entrez gene IDs for each pathway.
